          "description": "At 9th level, an arcane trickster can become invisible , as if under the effects of greater invisibility , as a free action. She can remain invisible for a number of rounds per day equal to her arcane trickster level. Her caster level for this effect is equal to her caster level. These rounds need not be consecutive."
